name: Shiridi SaiBaba
overview:
Set up in 2006, Shirdi Sai Baba Food Products have been one of the potent forces to reckon in the industry. We have always worked on full-scale production plan, which helps us to gain a strong foothold in the market. This has helped us to strengthen our stature as leading processor, exporter and supplier of Fresh Vegetables, Dry Fruits, Agro Products, LED Lights, Medicinal Herbs and many more. We follow a systematic approach that helps to understand the market growth and accordingly come up with strategies to establish our forte in the industry.

Client Satisfaction: We strive for maximum client satisfaction, which results in maximum business for us. Our clients keep coming back to us, which indicates that we have earned lot of name in the industry, serving with earnest quality and timeliness of the orders.

Our Quality: The quality managers are well trained on each and every aspect of the product functionality so that these are tested as per the varied condition. They take part in regular conclaves, seminars and knowledge sharing platforms where in they are updated about the current advancements. These help to garner rich experience and produce high quality products.

Our Team: We have a highly skilled and efficient team possessing enormous industry knowledge and have skill set to execute big order. Every single individual is cross-trained to work on multiple platforms. This cross functionality helps to take bigger work order and thus contribute to company’s growth.

Our Infrastructure: Backed up with tremendous infrastructure support, we are able to execute our orders in a superior way. All the latest machines and equipment have helped in achieving the production output in a greater way. The excellent technological resources given to us have helped reap good returns. Due to methodological and structured approach we have earned accolades from all the quarters.
